1. How redirect the output to file
$ program [arguments...] 2>&1 | tee outfile

2. How to create a root account in Ubuntu 14.04
- login as root
$ sudo su -

- change the password of root
$ passwd

3. How to replace a word in every line at the beginning in VI editor
- open the file
- press ESC
- %s!^!< string name>
